Package com.tinkerpop.rexster

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSubResource
    Base "sub" resource class which contains helper methods for getting extensions, the RexsterApplicationGraph, and request object.
    Application
    Main class for initializing, starting and stopping Rexster.
    BaseResource
    Base resource from which most other resources extend.
    EdgeResource
    Resource for edges.
    GraphResource
    Resource for graphs.
    IndexResource
    Resource for graph indices.
    KeyIndexResource
    Key index resource.
    PrefixResource  
    RexsterApplicationGraph
    Holds a graph and its assigned extensions.
    RexsterMediaType
    Custom media types for rexster.
    RexsterResource
    Root resources for graphs in the REST API.
    RexsterResourceContext
    Context for a resource request.
    RootResource
    The root resources for Rexster which shows the splash page for Rexster as HTML.
    Tokens
    String tokens used by Rexster.
    VertexResource
    Vertex resource.
